      %ul
        %li TDD/BDD (rspec, cucumber, capybara)
        %li Build your own RubyGem
        %li Continuous Integration (CI)
      %br
      %h2 Day 3
      %ul
        %li RVM
        %li Advanced git
        %li Speedy Rails
        %li What's new in Rails 4
      %br
      %h2 Day 4
      %ul
        %li Authentication / Authorization / OAuth patterns
        %li Instrumentation (error handling, monitoring, logging, etc...)
        %li AJAX and Rails
        %li Mailers
      %br
      %h2 Day 5
      %ul
        %li Server configurations
        %li Scaling
        %li Deployments
